            . I live in <placeName id="t18310407-287-crimeloc1523">White Conduit-grove, Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310407-287-crimeloc1523" type="placeName" value="White Conduit-grove, Islington"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310407-287-crimeloc1523" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310407-287-off1521 t18310407-287-crimeloc1523"></join>. This bundle contains eight shirts belonging to me, two table-cloths, and the other articles stated - they are all mine, except what are my servants', Mary Jenkins; here is a gown, a shift, and night-gown of hers - they were all hanging in the yard behind my house on the evening of the 29th of March, and were missed at a quarter before nine o'clock - I know nothing of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>T. H. KING re-examined. Q. How far from the prosecutor's did you stop the prisoner? A.About three quarters of a mile - it was about half-past nine o'clock.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming down Maiden-lane, and a young man asked me to hold a bundle - directly I took it he ran away.</p>
               <p>T. H. KING. No, they were talking together, and she walked ten or fifteen yards before she caught sight of us; there were three more she impeached - the man has absconded ever since.</p>
